<svg viewBox="0 0 700 400" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width:100%;height:auto;background:#111113;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);margin:20px 0">
  <text x="20" y="30" fill="#fafafa" font-size="16" font-weight="700" font-family="sans-serif">Rhetoric vs. Legislation — a Timeline of Japan's Web3 Pledges</text>
  <text x="20" y="50" fill="#71717a" font-size="12" font-family="sans-serif">Per PM Takaichi's video address at WebX 2026 (July 13, 2026)</text>
  <rect x="20" y="72" width="660" height="46" rx="6" fill="#1f1a11" stroke="#92400e"/>
  <text x="35" y="92" fill="#fde68a" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="700">2022: Kishida cabinet issues "Web3 White Paper" — NFTs/DAOs as national strategy</text>
